
The research project aimed to analyze sunspot data to understand the frequency and power of solar flares. This involved comparing data from different groups to 
identify trends in flare occurrence and energy, contributing to better predictions of solar activity.

DOI: 10.3847/1538-4357/accc89

Press Release: https://www.colorado.edu/today/2023/05/09/how-1000-undergraduates-helped-solve-enduring-mystery-about-sun

